Given the following program and the variable in complex data type, decompose the it into variables with primary data type.. The program is typedef long a;
typedef a __attribute__((__vector_size__(sizeof(long)))) d;
fn1() {}
d fn2() {
  d f = {fn1};
  return f;
}
main() {}
.                 The target to be optimized is `d`: a vector type with size equal to the size of a `long` integer.
